data.description: MAULDIN - One-level brick ranch with 3BR, 2BA minutes from shopping and Interstate.  This home offers 1,700SqFt and sits on a spacious 0.57 acre lot with huge Cypress trees for privacy.  Step in to find an open living room which leads into the kitchen/breakfast area.  There is also a den/office area at the back making a great space for at-home office.  This is a split-BR plan with MBR on left side and 2BRs and BA on right side. There is space to have a half bath or to open up the hall to one of the full baths.  Backyard is partially fenced and includes 2 outbuildings and covered deck.  Assumable solar panels through SunRun.  SELLERS WILL PAY OFF SOLAR PANELS WITH AN ACCEPTABLE OFFER.  Power is $25/mo in summer and $52/mo in winter!  Come make this one home today!
